Opera Unite <-> KDE integration.

Sample use-cases:
#1: Right-click a file, select "Copy Unite URL". In no time the URL is in your clipboard.
#2: Make a screenshot. In KSnapshot, select "Open with", "unite-wrapper.sh"

Installation:
* Edit unite.desktop and set ~/src/kde_unite to the path where you have installed the script
* Copy unite.desktop to /usr/share/kde4/services/ServiceMenus
* Edit unite.py to set directories and URL
